description: Northeast facing 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom in the Seaport District's desirable FP3 building! Contemporary finishes throughout and an oversized window in the living room captures fantastic natural sunlight. The unit features a cozy entry way, graciously sized interior bedroom with transom glass allowing continuous flow of sunlight, and an oversized living space with functional floor plan and original building brick detail! Building amenities include 24hr concierge service and common roof deck with gas grill. Enjoy living within the Fort Point and dining at many of its fabulous restaurants including Row 34, Pastoral, Tavern Road and Blue Dragon. Did I mention, three of Chef Barbara Lynch's restaurants are located within the building? Drink, Sportello and Menton!
